    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, it breaks my heart a little to even think about parting with this beauty. She\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy\u2014kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered with the best products since day one. The paint has that deep, glass-like shine that makes you do a double-take in the driveway, and the interior still feels as fresh as the day she rolled off the lot. She drives like an absolute dream\u2014smooth, quiet, and incredibly responsive. I\u2019ve obsessed over every detail so you don\u2019t have to. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved and is ready for a new home, come on over, let\u2019s have a coffee, and I\u2019ll show you why this is the one you\u2019ve been waiting for!",
      "price": 44500.0,
